Romania rise two places at No 14 and could be seeded in July when European qualifying groups for the 2018 World Cup are drawn.

Costa Rica remain No 13 to lead CONCACAF nations. The United States falls one to No 32.

Algeria at No 18 lead the African nations. Iran are Asia's best at No 42. 

